CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1962, pg. C3, reads: "Photos of Your Pittsburgh Story Rally - Program Keys - Keys in program were singer Robert Mosley and Artless Martinez and Mrs. Daisy Lampkin, vice president of The Pittsburgh Courier who was chairman of the inspiring, successful Appreciation Day Rally."
TitMainTitle: Robert Mosley or Mosely, Daisy Lampkin, and Artless Martinez posed in Soldiers and Sailors Memorial Hall, for Pittsburgh Courier newspaper's Appreciation Day rally
